text: Up and at 'Em is a 1922 American romantic comedy movie directed by William A. Seiter and starring Doris May, Hallam Cooley, J. Herbert Frank, Otis Harlan. It was distributed by Film Booking Offices of America. ==Other websites== * * Category:1922 comedy movies Category:1922 romance movies Category:1920s romantic comedy movies Category:American romantic comedy movies Category:American silent movies Category:Movies directed by William A.
